title: Ansh: The Deadly Part
subTitle: An honest police officer dedicated to uprooting crime ruffles the feathers of corrupt politicians and criminals, who scheme to stop him.

title: Hum Types
subTitle: Despite different social classes, Charu and Makrand find unexpected common ground, as their growing connection reveals shared struggles and emotions.

title: Ahsaas
subTitle: After being rejected by their fathers, Raju and Anu elope and get settled in a village but when the parents learn about their whereabouts, they decide to bring them back.

title: Sita Ram Chaddha
subTitle: Sita Ram Chaddha's married daughter has the option to seek financial help from her brother. However, she has a unique request that transforms the lives of everyone.

title: Bahaar
subTitle: A young woman gets married, with the typical expectations of a blissful domestic life. However, her dreams turn into a nightmare when her mother-in-law constantly harasses and humiliates her solely because she has been unable to conceive after five years of marriage.

title: Woh Khaas
subTitle: A successful businessman decides to take a break from his mundane life and goes on a vacation. Furthermore, he happens to meet a stranger who transforms him.

title: Raah
subTitle: Raahis an exploration of the several stages of struggle when one steps out to pursue a dream. Sahir lives in Mumbai city with his family. The emotional and poetic narrative explores his faith, kinship and his struggle to establish himself.

title: Bepar
subTitle: On the surface, Indian immigrant Kritika and her Pakistani husband Faiz appear to be happily married. Underneath, however, their inter-faith union is caught in between love and cultural differences.

title: Expectations
subTitle: A boy struggles to grapple with his emotions because of expectations laid down by society and decides to take drastic measures.

title: Uyire Uyire
subTitle: Rahul and Priya meet during a trip to Goa and fall in love with each other. However, their lives take a turn when Rahul learns that Priya is the sibling of Shiva, who had once tortured his sister.

title: Girgit
subTitle: The true colours of public officials are revealed when the lens is focused beyond their scope of duty and instead on the selfish motivations for their insincere actions.

title: Hey Listen!
subTitle: Dhruv and Vidya get in touch and decide to meet each other a few years after their breakup. However, their meeting soon takes an unfortunate turn as old conflicts and emotions gradually come to the surface, causing them to get into a heated argument.

title: Wazir
subTitle: When his daughter is killed by the terrorist he is chasing, Daanish, a policeman, vows revenge. He finds a confidante in Pandit, a grandmaster, who is also mourning the loss of his daughter.

title: #Goals
subTitle: After some time apart, Meera and Ranbir find their relationship at a point where it becomes a perfect example of the shallowness and fragility of modern-day dating.

title: A Tale Of An Onion Witch Chapter 2
subTitle: A newlywed couple encounters a woman claiming to be Mangla, who cautions them about an ancient witch roaming the area at night in search of onions. However, the situation takes an unexpected turn when a young girl desperately seeks assistance by knocking on their door at the stroke of midnight, plunging the couple into a potentially perilous scenario.

title: Half Cake
subTitle: A poor single mother struggles fiercely to earn the extra money needed to fulfill her child's simple wish for a cake just like the one he saw in a shop.

title: Harshit
subTitle: Fate plays a twisted game with Harshit and Rahila, who are madly in love with each other.

title: Love Ishtory
subTitle: A man from an upper caste learns that his daughter is in love with a man from a lower caste. While he beats up the man, a police officer encourages him to continue his assault.

title: Pilibhit
subTitle: Siraj, a poor flute maker, resides in the forest of Pilibhit, known for its man-eating tigers. Soon, his poverty and the tragedies in his life threaten to break his values.

title: 10.30 Lets Go To School
subTitle: A determined village girl struggles to attend school as her family expects her to stay home, but her love for learning drives her to find clever ways to keep studying.

title: Dum Dum Deega Deega
subTitle: Ajju, the son of a drunkard beggar, lives on the streets of Mumbai but holds a positive outlook towards life. He refuses to beg and tries to earn money through respectable means.

title: Aakhri Kahani
subTitle: A desperate writer plans one final movie pitch to a producer. However, he ends up driving the producer in his taxi, giving him an unexpected opportunity to share his idea during the ride.

title: Abba Ki Chaddi
subTitle: A troubled housewife, weary and worn down by her husband's numerous past misdeeds, finally seeks the retribution she believes is long overdue.

title: In Your Arms
subTitle: After 14 years, Nikhil tells Payal he wants a divorce, confessing love for a colleague. Payal agrees, but only on one condition.

title: Love Bites
subTitle: Karthik and Meghna flaunt their hickeys, making their sexual chemistry obvious to everyone.

title: Panch Din
subTitle: A married couple, meeting in a caf√© to finalise their divorce, is unexpectedly joined by a mutual friend. However, they begin to rethink their decision after the friend reminds them of a past event.

title: Thanks Mom
subTitle: Two brothers, who are aspiring filmmakers, are forced to use their mother's fund to make their film. However, disagreements arise when their mother does not approve the contents of the film.

title: Dwand
subTitle: Ruby, raised to believe in her potential, however, finds herself married to a traditional man, Vivek. After motherhood, she decides to pursue an advertising career, sparking unforeseen troubles.

title: Once Upon A Time In Office
subTitle: Once Upon A Time In Office

title: Baggage
subTitle: Sara's twin sister disappears in a bizarre manner, leaving her to deal with the loss. However, when she is unable to come to terms with it, Sara decides to find answers.

title: Beyond Failing
subTitle: A young student struggles with academic pressure due to poor performance. However, she sets out on a path of self-discovery and soon finds her true passion.

title: Calling Bell
subTitle: A demented delivery man forces himself inside the house of a young lady, threatening to kill her. However, the confrontation takes an unusual turn when the true nature of his visit is revealed.

title: Saanjh
subTitle: SAANJH tells the story of Shyam and Sandhya, childhood friends who meet for the last time. Shyam loves Sandhya, but she sees him only as a friend. We surprisingly learn that Shyam is actually struggling with mental disorder, and Sandhya is nothing but just in his imagination. Despite the calm riverbank setting, Shyam's inner struggles are evident. As Shyam faces reality, he realizes he must accept things as they are, showing the power of love and understanding ourselves.

title: Life 2.0
subTitle: A nature lover pushes her ambitious human resettlement proposal to a world that is not ready for it. However, a data-related catastrophe may change everything.

title: Khalish
subTitle: A girl whose childhood is marred by violent household disputes grows up feeling helpless and anxious, developing hostility towards authority and triggering colossal consequences.

title: Duty
subTitle: Individuals from different walks of life and social classes demonstrate the interdependence of each social stratum on the other through their duties and responsibilities.

title: Choices
subTitle: Just one day before their wedding, Ritesh confesses something to Yami that threatens to change the course of their relationship.

title: Destiny's Two
subTitle: A man newly married to a dwarf decides to go to a red-light area to fulfill his desire for a taller woman.

title: Charitra Varnan
subTitle: A cab driver's kind attempt to help a weeping woman who dashed out of her house after a fight with her husband goes terribly wrong.

title: Girl in Red
subTitle: A writer who is struggling with writer's block is in search of a story. However, he lands himself in trouble when he stumbles upon a deadly secret while talking to his garbage collector.

title: Harmless
subTitle: A boy in need of money to make it big in life and a girl who is looking for thrill concoct a plan and stage a kidnapping to extort money from the girl's rich father.

title: Laxmi
subTitle: A maid is shocked to find the owner of the house where she works dead. Upon telling her partner, he plans a scheme to rob the house.
